The paper discusses a data dissemination platform that supports data security and privacy levels, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The platform is designed for cloud-based applications, which suggests a focus on distributed computing (cs.DC) and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also mentions smart grids and IoT environments, indicating a potential focus on information retrieval (cs.IR) and databases (cs.DB).
